[Coder] Se crea una herramienta para raspado de citas desde quotes.toscrape.com y guardado en un archivo JSON.

Herramienta usada: scrape_quotes
Args: {}
Resultado: {'ok': True, 'file_path': 'quotes.json'}

[Contexto] Preferencias y ranking de tools:
```json
{
  "top_tools": "- scrape_quotes: score=0.600, ok=1/1, avg_ms=3493",
  "user_prefs": {}
}
```

[Coder] Se necesita leer el archivo 'quotes.json' generado por el scraping, validar que sea JSON v√°lido y devolver una muestra representativa del contenido.

Herramienta usada: read_json_file
Args: {'file_path': 'quotes.json'}
Resultado: {'ok': True, 'file_path': 'quotes.json', 'num_records': 100, 'sample': [{'text': '‚ÄúThe world as we have created it is a process of our thinking. It cannot be changed without changing our thinking.‚Äù', 'author': 'Albert Einstein', 'tags': ['change', 'deep-thoughts', 'thinking', 'world']}, {'text': '‚ÄúIt is our choices, Harry, that show what we truly are, far more than our abilities.‚Äù', 'author': 'J.K. Rowling', 'tags': ['abilities', 'choices']}, {'text': '‚ÄúThere are only two ways to live your life. One is as though nothing is a miracle. The other is as though everything is a miracle.‚Äù', 'author': 'Albert Einstein', 'tags': ['inspirational', 'life', 'live', 'miracle', 'miracles']}]}
